Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:49.78,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}忘記你的所有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:55.81,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}就能繼續向前嗎？
